Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.54,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To sink or swim {\fsp1}生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}dog eat dog world {\fsp1}だと言い聞かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:56.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.84,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Survival of the fittest {\fsp1}弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If it's the world that our wisdom will lead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.85,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Then tell me what went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.40,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've paid my dues
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.19,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've sold my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.07,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So tell me, what is left for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}when I've given up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.78,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:27.25,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:37.55,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.97,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:47.52,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.06,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:57.61,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.15,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}真実の見えない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.66,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}善と悪のバランスを保ち
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.16,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}殺すか殺されるかの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.70,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ちっぽけな世界なのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:13.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}おい　誰か答えてみてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.59,op-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.54,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是沉是浮 为了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉他 这是同类相残的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:56.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.84,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2)}适者生存 弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果智慧能引领这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.85,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就告诉我 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.40,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已付出太多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.19,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已出卖灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉我 如果我放弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又能够得到些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.78,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 这是个怎样的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:27.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看过太多风景 却毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:37.55,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了追寻那个风景 我是否已毫无感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 这是个怎样的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:47.52,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看过太多风景 却毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.06,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:57.61,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了追寻那个风景 我是否已毫无感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.15,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看不见真相的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.66,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}维持善恶的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.16,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀或被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.70,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这世界难道这么无趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:13.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 谁能回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:13.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
